WEBVTT

00:03:27.731 --> 00:03:30.914
those last tens of millions
will have been raised up

00:03:30.938 --> 00:03:32.404
above that threshold.

00:03:32.958 --> 00:03:35.285
So it's a miracle, actually,
in our lifetime.

00:03:36.188 --> 00:03:37.378
Hard to believe.

00:03:37.402 --> 00:03:40.155
But brute facts are even harder to ignore.

00:03:41.069 --> 00:03:44.555
A nation that didn't even appear
on any of the international league tables

00:03:44.579 --> 00:03:45.895
25 years ago

00:03:45.919 --> 00:03:47.371
has soared,

00:03:47.395 --> 00:03:50.664
to rival -- and in some areas,
surpass -- the United States.

00:03:54.964 --> 00:03:58.060
Thus, the challenge
that will shape our world:

00:03:58.924 --> 00:04:02.418
a seemingly unstoppable rising China